{"type": "article", "id": 6061, "title": "Remix x Casio G-Shock 10周年限量腕表", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-10T07:48:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234010egN7P0Ao2VH3Zxul.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;-webkit-text-stroke-color:#000000;-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">\r\n\tCasio G-Shock 最近携手台湾街头品牌 Remix Clothing 推出了 10 周年限量款联名腕表 DW-6900RM-1。设计团队以 G-Shock 经典的 6900 表款为蓝本进行再创作，沿用了黑色系的主色调，并赋予了表腕 10 周年专属 logo 。表盘两侧的 4 个按钮采用黑色离子 IP 处理。此外，双方还共同为 DW-6900RM-1 配置了一款做工精致的木制收纳盒，低调内敛中散发出藏不住的奢华。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234008lBS7aTV1tvqP5YbN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234008adDhogLyBEU9rl2P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234008HbQNkKt8pjWSe9ER.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234009PwW1lXRD6dcFYGyS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234009uyVs3NntfOMXdRSI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}